Introduction
------------
The Guanxi Common Lite module provides shared services to the other Guanxi modules
such as the Identity Provider and Service Provider. It has no dependencies other
than the standard Java libraries. For security and crytopgrahic functionality, the
Guanxi Common module should be used.

Building
--------
git clone http://github.com/guanxi/guanxi-common-lite.git
cd guanxi-common-lite
mvn clean install

More information
----------------
The Guanxi blog: http://codebrane.com/blog/?cat=2

